[{"type":"{{","value":[["pagebanner"],["Pagebanner default.jpg"],["pgname=Weaverville"]]},"\n",{"type":"'''","value":[{"type":"[","value":["http:\/\/www.visitweaverville.com\/ Weaverville"]}]}," is a town in the ",{"type":"[[","value":[["North Carolina Mountains"]]},".\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Get in"]},"\n",{"type":"===","value":["By plane"]},"\nThe ",{"type":"'''","value":["Asheville Regional Airport"]}," (",{"type":"{{","value":[["IATA"],["AVL"]]},") ",{"type":"[","value":["http:\/\/www.flyavl.com\/"]}," offers jet and commuter service on US Airways, Delta Air Lines, and United Airlines and has direct flights from ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Atlanta"]]},", ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Charlotte"]]},", ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Cincinnati"]]},", ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Detroit"]]},", ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Houston"]]},", ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Minneapolis"]]},"\/",{"type":"[[","value":[["St. Paul"]]},", ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Newark (New Jersey)"],["Newark, NJ"]]},", and ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Orlando"]]},". It is located fifteen miles south of downtown Asheville near the town of Fletcher. Ground transportation and major rental car companies are available at the airport terminal.\n\nFlights into ",{"type":"'''","value":["Greenville-Spartanburg International Airport"]}," (",{"type":"{{","value":[["IATA"],["GSP"]]},") ",{"type":"[","value":["http:\/\/www.gspairport.com\/"]}," located in ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Greenville (South Carolina)"],["Greenville, South Carolina"]]},", ",{"type":"'''","value":["Charlotte Douglas International Airport"]}," (CLT) ",{"type":"[","value":["http:\/\/www.charlotteairport.com"]}," located in ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Charlotte"],["Charlotte, North Carolina"]]},", or ",{"type":"'''","value":[{"type":"[","value":["http:\/\/www.tys.org\/ McGhee Tyson Airport (TYS)"]}]}," located in ",{"type":"[[","value":[["Knoxville"],["Knoxville, Tennessee"]]},", are sometimes cheaper than flying directly to Asheville.  Greenville is about a 1.5 hour drive, Charlotte and Knoxville are both about 2 hour drives.\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Get around"]},"\nLike most of Western North Carolina, you do need a car to get to and from Weaverville.  Once on Main Street, it's an easy walk to much of the shopping, restaurants, and accommodations in the area.  Limited bus service to and from Asheville is also available.\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["See"]},"\n",{"type":"*","value":[" ",{"type":"{{","value":[["see"],["name=Vance Birthplace"],["url=http:\/\/www.ah.dcr.state.nc.us\/sections\/hs\/vance\/vance.htm"],["email=vance@ncmail.net"],["address=911 Reems Creek Rd"],["lat="],["long="],["directions="],["phone = +1 828 645-6706"],["tollfree="],["fax="],["hours=Apr-Oct Tu-Sa 9AM-5PM; Nov-Mar Tu-Sa 10AM-4PM"],["price="],["content="]]}]},"\nLearn more about visiting the Vance Birthplace at ",{"type":"[","value":["http:\/\/www.nchistoricsites.org\/vance Vance Birthplace"]},"\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Do"]},"\n\n",{"type":"*","value":[" ",{"type":"{{","value":[["do"],["name=Art in Autumn"],["url=http:\/\/www.artinautumn.com"],["email="],["address=Main Street"],["lat="],["long="],["directions="],["phone="],["tollfree="],["fax="],["hours=10AM-5PM"],["price="],["content=Art in Autumn showcases a diverse range of juried Art and Craft with over 100 artists and craftspeople. Also features food and music, free admission and free parking."]]}]},{"type":"*","value":[" ",{"type":"{{","value":[["do"],["name=Christmas Candlelight Stroll"],["url=http:\/\/www.visitweaverville.com\/candlelight"],["email="],["address=Main Street"],["lat="],["long="],["directions="],["phone="],["tollfree="],["fax="],["hours=6-9PM"],["price="],["content=Make plans to join us as Weaverville will be aglow with luminaries along the streets, local choirs and bands will provide music, and horse and buggy rides will be available through town. Local businesses will be open late for Christmas shopping. Kids can visit with Santa and decorate their own cookies